  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to further define the appropriate population for Pico-Salax, a purgative used
      prior to colonoscopy. Patients over the age of 70 years with normal renal function scheduled
      for colonoscopy will receive Pico-Salax and have pre and post preparation bloodwork and
      electrocardiograms (ECGs).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
